INSERT INTO `sentence` VALUES (4011, '2001考研英语', 'I have been transformed from a passionate advocate of the philosophy of \"having it all\", preached by Linda Kelsey for the past seven years in the pages of She magazine, into a woman who is happy to settle for a bit of everything.', '在过去的七年里，琳达·凯尔西在《她》杂志的版面上一直宣扬“拥有一切”的哲学，现在，我已经从一个充满激情的倡导者转变成一个乐于满足于一切事物的女人。');
