INSERT INTO `sentence` VALUES (4937, '2009考研英语', '\" One wonders what Dane thought of the careful sermons explaining the Bible that he heard in puritan churched.', '有人想知道Dane在清教徒教堂里听到的解释圣经的训诫。');
INSERT INTO `sentence` VALUES (4938, '2009考研英语', 'Meanwhile, many settles had slighter religious commitments than Dane\'s, as one clergyman learned in confronting folk along the coast who mocked that they had not come to the New world for religion.', '同时，许多定居点的宗教承诺比丹尼的要少，正如一位牧师在面对沿海的民众时学到的，这些人嘲笑他们没有来新世界寻求宗教信仰。');
