INSERT INTO `sentence` VALUES (5164, '2010考研英语二', 'a brief introduction to the political scientist Andrew Hacker   Over the past decade, many companies had perfected the art of creating automatic behaviors — habits — among consumers.', '对政治学家安德鲁·哈克的简要介绍在过去的十年里，许多公司已经完善了在消费者中创造自动行为——习惯——的艺术。');
INSERT INTO `sentence` VALUES (5165, '2010考研英语二', 'These habits have helped companies earn billions of dollars when customers eat snacks, apply lotions and wipe counters almost without thinking, often in response to a carefully designed set of daily cues.', '这些习惯帮助公司赚取了数十亿美元时，客户吃零食，应用乳液和擦拭柜台几乎不假思索，往往响应精心设计的一套日常线索。');
